1. in EC2
2. click launch template 
3. select os image 
4. instance type t2.micro
5. select keypair 
6. select subnet
7.then security group select existing 
8. click launch template
9. then select template name  goto action  select launch instance form template  go bydefault  
10. now click launch instance
11. select the instance  goto action  select image and templates  select create image
12. image name AMItemplate1  go bydefault  click create image
13. now, goto AMIs 
